# babystack injects connection env into your test/dev/agent process at runtime — you do NOT set these by
# hand. This file documents the shape of what your app will read (exactly like production).
#
# Populated automatically by @babystack/vitest (globalSetup) or the `baby` CLI. Never commit a real .env.

# DATABASE_URL=mysql://app:app@127.0.0.1:<auto>/app_test
# REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:<auto>
# S3_ENDPOINT=http://127.0.0.1:<auto>
# AWS_ENDPOINT_URL=http://127.0.0.1:4566
